# Verification policy

- Before stating "tests pass" or "deploy is green", run `npm run test:static` at minimum.
- If the change touches `cases/src/assets/js/**` or `cases/src/assets/casey/**` or `cases/scripts/**`, run `npm test` (not only static tests).
- When possible, mention the exact command run in the response (static vs full).

